title: UDYR MONTAGE PATCH 6.12

embed.description: Playing Udyr jungle in Season 6 patch 6.12 haha, hope you guys enjoy this new type of montage we put together :D!, went with Cinderhulk this time for some tankiness :), it is very good to clear jungle creatures really quickly, but would love to try full ad or even full ap!

body:
Hey guys, made a little Funtage :D, Hope you guys enjoy!!

Any bit of feedback is appreciated :)!
